### Saare students dekho
GET http://localhost:3000/api/students

###

### Subject filter ke saath students dekho
GET http://localhost:3000/api/students?subject=Python

###

### Ek student ID se dekho
GET http://localhost:3000/api/students/1

###

### ID jo exist nahi karta — 404 check
GET http://localhost:3000/api/students/99

###

### Naya student add karo
POST http://localhost:3000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Hafizullah",
  "marks": 78,
  "subject": "JavaScript"
}

###

### Incomplete data bhejo — 400 error dekhne ke liye
POST http://localhost:3000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User"
}

###

### Pass list dekho
GET http://localhost:3000/api/pass-list